-- Gatwick Funding Said to Hire Banks for Planned Pound Bond Sale
-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n   a n d   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 2012-01-12T10:18:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/gatwick-funding-said-to-hire-banks-for-planned-pound-bond-sale.html
Gatwick Funding Ltd. hired  Credit
Agricole SA (ACA) ,  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA) , Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc
and Societe Generale SA to manage a benchmark senior bond sale
in pounds, which will be completed when market conditions allow,
according to a banker and investor with knowledge of the plan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hannah Benjamin in London at 
